reviews.text: Good service and experience and by ops Mukesh Vishwakarma

Excellent Services are too good and satisfactory

Thanks to Mr Mukesh Vishwakarma

I got a chance to visit the Ujjain branch. The service was amazing. The request was served with good care, and I didn’t have to wait for long.

It's sad to see poor service from the Ujjain office staff (Mukesh Vishwakarma) as my application for a matured insurance policy payout got rejected, and when one of my relatives went to check on the status, he seemed to be busy and justified by stating that the signature did not match and hence got rejected. I live abroad and cannot come frequently to the branch to perform the KYC. When I asked, can you update my email or contact details which are incorrectly entered in the system. He said, "This is not required as your insurance will be paid and it is not necessary". Sadly, the staff is not trained enough to do all the due diligence and perform all the necessary checks at the time when the application is requested. I did a similar thing at ICICI Bank, and I received the payout in 3 working days.

It's hard to recommend anybody to go to Bajaj Alliance.
